.TH ox-explain 1  "ox-explain " 
.SH NAME
ox\-explain \- Show the full dependency chain for a target
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBox\-explain\fR [\fB\-\-json\fR] [\fB\-f\fR|\fB\-\-file\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fITARGET\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Show the full dependency chain for a target
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-json\fR
Output JSON instead of human\-readable text
.TP
\fB\-f\fR, \fB\-\-file\fR \fI<FILE>\fR [default: Oxymakefile.toml]
Oxymakefile path
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fITARGET\fR>
The output file path or job ID to explain
